CQF Financing Options
Making the investment in the CQF is a career-changing decision. With our new financing options for self-funded residents of the USA or Canada that decision is now easier to make, as you can choose to either spread the payments over time or pay in full prior to the start of the program.
Summary of Financing Options
Full program
24-month plan
Deposit + 23 monthly installments
Level 1 or Level 2
11-month plan
Deposit + 10 monthly installments

For more details and a full breakdown of costs, contact Tim Johnson for details.
All figures are paid in US dollars. Student scholarships are also available.
Note: The fees quoted above are applicable to the January 2019 Program.